 - Accept a context parameter in its constructor
 - Use SharedPreferences to save and load pet data
 - Add methods to save pets when changes are made
 - Load pets from storage when the repository is initialized

3. I also updated the `PetHoodApplication` class to pass the application context to the `AdoptionPetRepository` constructor.

